txt.en: 'Protect me! We must do as the Ever-seer commands! Spread out!'
'You impress Eldgang.'
'Fool! You have failed and brought the intruders right to us!'
'They must not be allowed to enter Norbar! Stop them at all cost...ha! You will need my aid.'
'You have interfered for the last time! I will make certain you go no further!'
'We cannot defeat him alone! Only the hottest flames will destroy him!'
'You there, little one! You are not like the Ghâshfra...have you come to help the Eldgang?'
'The first Eldgang came here after the Great Destruction when this city fell into the earth. They made it their home, and now it is our home, too.'
'There was great evil here when my people came, and it remains, though imprisoned...'
'Thank you, little ones.'
'But the Ghâshfra, the Fire-orcs, seek to unleash the Great Evil and use it against us.'
'Well done.  Trust in you was smart of Eldgang.'
'We fight the Ghâshfra, but they are many.'
'Will you help us? If you fight the Ghâshfra, I must warn you to beware the Ever-seer....'
Thrâng enters the fray!
'They are coming, Eimyr, as I told you they would. The little ones approach.'
'Glathlírel knows nothing! What has she ever done but enslave you? You must deal with the little people now!'
'Why is it that you destroy my forces?'
'You will pay for that!'
'This will make things much tougher!'
'ENOUGH!'
'You are only delaying your death, fools!'
'Deal with them! I must see to our friend.'
'You slay the Orcs as well?  Why?  What is this?'
'The Ever-seer said you help Orcs!  Why you not help Orcs?'
'I am confused!  Perhaps you are not enemy he says!'
Injured Ranger
'Why do you kill the Eldgang's enemy?  Are you then friends?'
'You move like we do.  I will call you friend.'
'My pets, destroy them!'
'The Ever-seer has lied to us! He betrayed us from the beginning! He must not be allowed to escape.'
'I have seen enough. The time of the Eldgang ends now! Run for your lives if you wish to save yourself!'
'I am...confused. They never brought harm before. Glathírel said....'
'We will do as you say then, Ever-seer. You have protected us so far.'
'You have led the Orcs to us, little ones! The Ever-Seer spoke true! You are not to be trusted!'
'I call forth more help!  To me, darklings!  Arise from the shadows!'
Hi!
'Eldgang thank you, [placeholder].  Please speak to us if you need help, little ones.'
'Stop them! Everyone focus on the intruders!'
